<h1>Future Prospects - All Decisions Made</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @student.full_name %>,</p>

<p>This email is to inform you that your have received decisions on the following
  <%= pluralize @application.course_selections_count, 'course' %>:</p>

<ul>
  <% @application.course_selections.each do |selection| %>
      <li><%= link_to selection.course.title, course_url(selection.course) %> &mdash; <%= selection.course.college.name %> </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Next, you need to <%= link_to 'sign in', new_student_session_url %> to Future Prospects to view what the decisions
  are, you can then proceed to make your own choices.</p>

<p>You must do this before <strong><%= format_date @application.reply_date %></strong> or your application will be rejected.</p>

<p>Sincerely,
  <br><br>
  Future Prospects</p>
